{fontWeight}} text-[{{textColor}}] mb-1\" contenteditable=\"true\">Familiäre Atmosphäre</h3>\n              <p class=\"text-sm text-[{{textColor}}]/60 {{fontSize}}\" contenteditable=\"true\">Man kennt sich, man hilft sich – echte Community</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          \n          <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\">\n            <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-[{{primaryColor}}]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\">\n              <i class=\"fa-solid fa-dumbbell text-[{{primaryColor}}] text-xl\"></i>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n              <h3 class=\"{{fontWeight}} text-[{{textColor}}] mb-1\" contenteditable=\"true\">Oldschool-Atmosphäre</h3>\n              <p class=\"text-sm text-[{{textColor}}]/60 {{fontSize}}\" contenteditable=\"true\">Robuste Geräte, pures Training – kein Schnickschnack</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          \n          <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\">\n            <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-[{{primaryColor}}]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\">\n              <i class=\"fa-solid fa-smile text-[{{primaryColor}}] text-xl\"></i>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n              <h3 class=\"{{fontWeight}} text-[{{textColor}}] mb-1\" contenteditable=\"true\">Entspannte Stimmung</h3>\n              <p class=\"text-sm text-[{{textColor}}]/60 {{fontSize}}\" contenteditable=\"true\">Kein unangenehmes Gefühl – jeder trainiert auf seinem Level</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>"
